'''艾列克·湯瑪斯·米爾斯'''（{{lang-en|Alec Thomas Mills}}，{{bd|1991年|11月30日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於芝加哥小熊。[[2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，他在第22輪被皇家隊選走。2020年9月13日，他在大聯盟生涯第五場先發投出無安打比賽。
==職業生涯==
===堪薩斯市皇家===
2012年，大學還沒畢業的米爾斯便投身選秀，並在第22輪被皇家隊看中選進。<ref name=drafted>{{Cite web|url=http://archive.theleafchronicle.com/article/20120606/SPORTS/306060032/Montgomery-Central-product-drafted|title=Montgomery Central product drafted}}</ref>他從高階新人聯盟起步，平均一年升上一個聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.rockies.mlb.com/news/article/157821672/rockies-john-axford-designated-for-assignment|title=Rockies' John Axford designated for assignment|website=MLB.com|access-date=May 19, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125731/http://m.rockies.mlb.com/news/article/157821672/rockies-john-axford-designated-for-assignment|archive-date=March 4, 2016}}</ref>2016年5月18日，當時還在2A的米爾斯被皇家隊叫上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160517&content_id=178560470&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb|title=Texas notes: Mills making most of his shot {{!}} MiLB.com|access-date=May 19, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518111715/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160517&content_id=178560470&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb|archive-date=May 18, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kansascity.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/k-zone/article78390817.html|title=Royals summon pitcher Alec Mills as 26th player for doubleheader
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625085717/https://www.kansascity.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/k-zone/article78390817.html|archive-date=June 25, 2016}}</ref>他在初登板投了3.1局失5分。<ref name="auto1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/millsal02.shtml|title=Alec Mills Stats|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2021-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509223319/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/millsal02.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年2月8日，皇家將他放進指定讓渡名單內。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/02/royals-designate-alec-mills-for-assignment.html|title=Royals Designate Alec Mills For Assignment|last=Adams|first=Steve|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=February 8, 2017|accessdate=February 8, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209132212/http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/02/royals-designate-alec-mills-for-assignment.html|archive-date=February 9, 2017}}</ref>
===芝加哥小熊===
同一天，皇家將他交易至小熊，換來小聯盟球員Donnie Dewees。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.royals.mlb.com/news/article/215541392/royals-acquire-donnie-dewees-from-cubs/|title=Royals acquire Dewees in exchange for Mills|work=MLB.com|date=February 8, 2017|accessdate=February 8, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075632/http://m.royals.mlb.com/news/article/215541392/royals-acquire-donnie-dewees-from-cubs/|archive-date=February 11, 2017}}</ref>他在經過一年的養傷後，<ref name=iowa>{{cite web|url=https://www.desmoinesregister.com/story/sports/baseball/iowa-cubs/2018/06/22/alec-mills-iowa-cubs-chicago-cubs-milb-kansas-city-royals/727397002/ |title=How Iowa pitcher Alec Mills got better in 2017 despite missing most of the season |publisher=Desmoinesregister.com |date= |accessdate=September 13, 2020}}</ref>於2018年重返大聯盟。因為Tyler Chatwood受傷，所以球隊讓米爾斯嘗試先發。他也在他初次先發的比賽中敲出大聯盟首安。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-tyler-chatwood-20180823-story.html|title=Cubs place Tyler Chatwood on DL, select Alec Mills to pitch Friday|work=chicagotribune.com|date=August 24, 2018|accessdate=August 24, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824045449/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-tyler-chatwood-20180823-story.html|archive-date=August 24, 2018}}</ref>2019年，他大多都在小聯盟。他在3A投出6勝4敗，防禦率5.11。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=mills-000ale|title=Alec Mills Minor & Fall Leagues Statistics & History|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111210027/https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=mills-000ale|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年，因為[[荷西·昆塔納|荷西·昆塔納]]受傷，因此米爾斯遞補進入先發輪值中。9月13日，他在客場面對釀酒人投出小熊隊史第16場無安打比賽。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/alec-mills-throws-chicago-cubs-first-no-hitter-since-2016/|title=Alec Mills throws Chicago Cubs' first no-hitter since 2016|website=CBSSports.com|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218074724/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/alec-mills-throws-chicago-cubs-first-no-hitter-since-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他拿下5勝5敗，防禦率4.48。<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2020-standard-pitching.shtml|title=2020 National League Standard Pitching|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131042315/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2020-standard-pitching.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他平均每9局會被敲出1.9支全壘打，為國聯投手最多。<ref name="auto"/>
